APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW

2006-0104. C.R. Green, L.P. v. Mayfield Hts.

Cuyahoga App. No. 85853, 2005-Ohio-6359. Discretionary appeal accepted on Proposition of Law Nos. I and II.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., would also accept on all other Propositions of Law. Pfeifer, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., dissent.
